                                                                                                     Q ${g.centerX} ${g.bangsLengthY + 1} ${g.centerX - g.bangsDx} ${g.bangsLengthY}
                                                                                                     Q ${g.centerX - Math.max(g.bangsRootDx, g.bangsDx) - 6} ${(g.bangsRootY + g.bangsLengthY)/2} ${g.centerX - g.bangsRootDx} ${g.bangsRootY}`} 
